data.description: Seller offering $5,000 towards buyers closing costs!! Spacious Surrey Hills home boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a study boasting over 2,100 SF! The home has many recent updates including New Class 4 Impact Resistant Roof, newer AC, freshly painted, bathroom remodels, etc. There is an oversized office/bonus room directly off of the entry of the home. The living room is exceptionally large with beams along the ceiling and a brick fireplace with built ins! The primary bedroom has plenty of space, a walk-in closet, and a recently remodeled bathroom. The spare bedrooms are both very good sized w/ large closets. The backyard is fully fenced with raised flower beds! Price drop to highlight new professional photos taken after updates were made!
